entry.tran: 无与伦比的；无可匹敌的；超凡绝伦的
entry.def: If you describe something as unsurpassed, you are emphasizing that it is better or greater than anything else of its kind.

example.ex: The quality of Smallbone furniture is unsurpassed.
example.tran: 斯莫尔本恩家具品质超凡。

example.ex: ...the Hamburg weekly, surely unsurpassed in the world for its intellectual range and quality.
example.tran: 在汉堡出版的这份周刊视野广博，见解深刻，无疑卓绝于世
